  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of a Market for Energy Efficient Lighting, Air Conditioners and Refrigerators in Costa Rica</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Energy diagnosis to identify and prioritize opportunities to replace conventional appliances with energy efficient appliances in highest energy consuming public institutions,2. Training and information program for market actors on the country&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s obligations to only procure energy efficient lighting and appliances and on mechanisms for product compliance.,3. Establishment of a revolving fund (RLF) for the financing of large-scale replacement programs in the public sector.,4. Development of capacities for environmentally sound end-of-life integrated management of lighting, refrigeration and air conditioning appliances.,Audits and Evaluations</narrative>
  </description>
